   300	- Top-line read: <2-3 sentences on whether premise-bleed is pervasive, localized, or absent>
   301	- Step-2 escalation triggered: yes (Class C ≥ 1) | no (no Class C)
   302	
   303	# §1. Per-instance findings
   304	
   305	For each premise-bleed instance:
