   316	- **Disposition implication (Class C only):** <which incubation axis (§5.1 / §5.2 / §5.3 / §5.4) this affects + how>
   317	- **Propagation sample (if applicable):** <slice-output section sampled per §5.2.5; verbatim citation; cumulative cap-tracking>
   318	
   319	# §2. Cross-artifact propagation patterns
   320	
   321	- Pattern 1: <description + propagation chain across artifacts>
   322	- Pattern 2: <...>
   323	
