.planning/gsd-2-uplift/audits/2026-04-28-cross-vendor-codebase-understanding-audit/wave-1/wave-1-scout-01-topology-runtime.md:163:Provisional delta note for `82bcf6b71..bf1d8aad0`: the broad topology/runtime map above remains usable, but two runtime details are fresher on `origin/main`.
