   168	## §3. Project-anchoring — where does arxiv-sanity-mcp sit?
   169	
   170	This is the question the framing arc has not yet answered. INITIATIVE.md `:50-58` records the operating frame as "uplift gsd-2 [...] toward the goal in §1" without anchoring to arxiv-sanity-mcp's specific context. The capabilities probe deliberately framed production-fitness in generic terms. Slices 1-5 are characterizing gsd-2 in the abstract.
   171	
