   294	  - **(b) Does the §1.4 release/breaking-change machinery-vs-practice gap shift the metaquestion answer for any specific context (per §5.3) where release-discipline is load-bearing?** Both syntheses flag this as direction-shifter for stable-extension-surface work; whether it actually shifts depends on first-target-shape.
