.planning/gsd-2-uplift/orchestration/audit-spec.md:135:## §6. Recommendation
.planning/gsd-2-uplift/orchestration/audit-spec.md:139:- **Minor findings → addendum.** Findings exist but don't change synthesis-relevant claims; addendum to slice output captures them; synthesis proceeds.
.planning/gsd-2-uplift/orchestration/audit-spec.md:140:- **Material findings → re-dispatch.** Findings change synthesis-relevant claims; re-dispatch slice with strengthened prompt; integrate audit notes into the re-dispatch's prompt.
