.planning/gsd-2-uplift/orchestration/slice-03-workflow-surface.md:48:## What "good slice 3 output" looks like
.planning/gsd-2-uplift/orchestration/slice-03-workflow-surface.md:51:- Q1 (commands list) is foundational for downstream slices; be exhaustive within reason. If gsd-2 has 20+ commands, list them in a table; if 5-10, list them prosaically.
